Loading DataSet into Power BI Desktop


 1. Open Power BI Desktop

     2. Click on Get Data

     3. Select SQL Server

     4. Add Server name (hypv8669.hostedbyappliedi.net) and click ok

     5. Select Database(ColaberryPowerBIReporting) , password (Colaberry99) and table

        (Class retention)

     6. Load
